{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":false,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"<xsl:decimal-format>","mdn_url":"/en-US/docs/Web/XSLT/Element/decimal-format","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div style=\"background:#f5f5f5; margin: 5px 0;\" id=\"sect1\">\n    <b><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/XSLT/Transforming_XML_with_XSLT/The_Netscape_XSLT_XPath_Reference\">XSLT/XPath Reference</a></b>: <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/XSLT/Element\">XSLT elements</a>, <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/EXSLT\">EXSLT functions</a>, <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/XPath/Functions\">XPath functions</a>, <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/XPath/Axes\">XPath axes</a>\n</div>\n<p>The <code>&lt;xsl:decimal-format&gt;</code> element defines the characters and symbols that are to be used in converting numbers into strings using the <code>format-number( )</code> function.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"Syntax","isH3":true,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: xml notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token namespace\">xsl:</span>decimal-format</span>\n  <span class=\"token attr-name\">name</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span>NAME</span>\n  <span class=\"token attr-name\">decimal-separator</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span>CHARACTER</span>\n  <span class=\"token attr-name\">grouping-separator</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span>CHARACTER</span>\n  <span class=\"token attr-name\">infinity</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span>STRING</span>\n  <span class=\"token attr-name\">minus-sign</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span>CHARACTER</span>\n  <span class=\"token attr-name\">NaN</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span>STRING</span>\n  <span class=\"token attr-name\">percent</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span>CHARACTER</span>\n  <span class=\"token attr-name\">per-mille</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span>CHARACTER</span>\n  <span class=\"token attr-name\">zero-digit</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span>CHARACTER</span>\n  <span class=\"token attr-name\">digit</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span>CHARACTER</span>\n  <span class=\"token attr-name\">pattern-separator</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span>CHARACTER</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">/&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"required_attributes","title":"Required Attributes","isH3":true,"content":"<p>None.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"optional_attributes","title":"Optional Attributes","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n  <dt id=\"name\"><code>name</code></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Specifies a name for this format.</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"decimal-separator\"><code>decimal-separator</code></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Specifies the decimal point character. The default is (<code>.</code>).</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"grouping-separator\"><code>grouping-separator</code></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Specifies the thousands separator character. The default is (<code>,</code>).</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"infinity\"><code>infinity</code></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Specifies the string used to represent infinity. The default is the string \"<code>Infinity</code>\".</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"minus-sign\"><code>minus-sign</code></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Specifies the minus sign character. The default is the hyphen (<code>-</code>).</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"nan\"><code>NaN</code></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Specifies the string used when the value is not a number. The default is the string \"<code>NaN</code>\".</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"percent\"><code>percent</code></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Specifies the percentage sign character. The default is (<code>%</code>).</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"per-mille\"><code>per-mille</code></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Specifies the per thousand character. The default is (<code>‰</code>).</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"zero-digit\"><code>zero-digit</code></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Specifies the digit zero character. The default is (<code>0</code>).</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"digit\"><code>digit</code></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Specifies the character used in the format pattern to stand for a digit. The default is (<code>#</code>).</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"pattern-separator\"><code>pattern-separator</code></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Specifies the character separating positive and negative subpatterns in a format pattern. The default is the semicolon (<code>;</code>).</p>\n  </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"type","title":"Type","isH3":true,"content":"<p>Top-level, must be the child of <code>&lt;xsl:stylesheet&gt;</code> or <code>&lt;xsl:transform&gt;</code>.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"defined","title":"Defined","isH3":true,"content":"<p>XSLT, section 12.3.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"gecko_support","title":"Gecko support","isH3":true,"content":"<p>Supported as of 1.0 (Mozilla 1.0, Netscape 7.0).</p>"}}],"toc":[],"summary":"The <xsl:decimal-format> element defines the characters and symbols that are to be used in converting numbers into strings using the format-number( ) function.","popularity":0.0002,"modified":"2022-09-26T17:50:45.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"decimal-format","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"decimal-format","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"<xsl:decimal-format>","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"decimal-format","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"}],"source":{"folder":"en-us/web/xslt/element/decimal-format","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/content/blob/style/old/files/en-us/web/xslt/element/decimal-format/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/content/commit/d169fd2b21950bc0c0976ebbee74054692e33162","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web","title":"Web technology for developers"},{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web/XSLT","title":"XSLT: Extensible Stylesheet Language Transformations"},{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web/XSLT/Element","title":"XSLT elements reference"},{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web/XSLT/Element/decimal-format","title":"<xsl:decimal-format>"}],"pageTitle":"<xsl:decimal-format> - XSLT: Extensible Stylesheet Language Transformations | MDN","noIndexing":false}}